## 3. Button map (necessity audit — WALKTHROUGH §9 interrogates with this table)

| Page | Element | Linked task | What appears on press | 3-state (loading/empty/error) defined? | Verdict |
|-------|------|-----------|----------------|----------------------------------|------|
|  |  |  |  |  | required / suspect / remove |

- **An element with an empty linked-task cell = "suspect"** — justify it or remove it. AUDIT deadCandidates
  exemptions apply only to elements with a justification written in this table.

