## 5. Transition coverage list (every edge INTEGRATE wires and VERIFY replays by clicking)

```
home → detail        (row click)
home → settings      (gear icon)
detail → home        (breadcrumb)
```

- 100% coverage of this list = wiring complete. Wiring outside the list (arbitrary pill switchers etc.) is forbidden.
